<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:11:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“1948 年的创伤已被唤醒”：策展人希望将艺术带回以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</link><description>基布兹 Yad Mordechai 可能被描述为一个带有基布兹的纪念场所，而不是相反。自10月7日起，基布兹的美术馆已关闭。它的馆长现在正在寻找复兴它的方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:23:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列矿业巨头丹·格特勒的斗争确凿无疑？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</link><description>根据 TheMarker 获得的记录，以色列商人丹·格特勒 (Dan Gertler) 显然透露了他如何规避美国因涉嫌在刚果行贿而实施的制裁，并隐瞒了一座价值 15 亿美元的铜钴矿。他的律师：“无意义的主张”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</guid></item><item><title>OPSEC失败：以色列军队在加沙的阵地在网上可见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</link><description>在犯了无数错误之后，以色列国防军发布了明确的指导方针，以防止敏感信息泄露。但这些并没有得到执行，以色列士兵在加沙作战时不断暴露自己的行动和立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部发现超罕见的白色彩虹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</link><description>白色彩虹不是在雨中而是在雾中观察到。就像彩虹一样，要看到彩虹，你需要在太阳身后看着雾气</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡克制地与哈马斯作战直到“全面胜利”是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡认为自己是温斯顿·丘吉尔，不断谈论与哈马斯的战争中的“全面胜利”。他拒绝接受的是，他实际上是二战角色扮演中的绥靖者内维尔·张伯伦。以色列公众对他的信任已从根本上被打破</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</guid></item><item><title>尽管内塔尼亚胡蔑视哈马斯的提议，但他为以色列谈判敞开了大门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</link><description>政治消息人士认为，总理的蔑视实际上可能为继续谈判奠定了基础。美国国务卿布林肯也表示，尽管哈马斯的回应存在问题，但它“为达成协议创造了空间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军预备役军官因在反政府集会上发表讲话而被停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-suspends-reservist-officer-for-speaking-at-anti-government-rally/0000018d-8798-d424-abad-9fd8466d0000</link><description>直到哈马斯袭击后战争爆发，约拉姆·布斯基拉中校暂停了预备役职务，以抗议内塔尼亚胡政府的司法改革。战争开始时他恢复了预备役职责</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 08:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-suspends-reservist-officer-for-speaking-at-anti-government-rally/0000018d-8798-d424-abad-9fd8466d0000</guid></item><item><title>根据战时规定，以色列在没有举行听证会的情况下将巴勒斯坦被拘留者关押了八天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</link><description>以色列国防军和警方依赖军法中很少使用的反恐条款，导致拘留期更长。在一个案件中，七人被关押了八天，直到法官裁定他们是犯罪受害者</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵被黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹炸伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-live/blinken-hamas-response-creates-space-for-agreement-netanyahu-slams-delusional-demands/0000018d-868c-d0de-af8d-8ebc4d630000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人向约旦河西岸军队哨所开枪，被以色列国防军打死 ■ 勇敢对布林肯：哈马斯的回应是为了确保以色列的拒绝，他们的立场将延长战争 ■ 联合国秘书长对以色列国防军预计向拉法推进感到“震惊”，布林肯警告内塔尼亚胡和勇敢事件 ■ 哈马斯寻求在135天停火提案中交换囚犯、人质以及以色列军队撤军</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-live/blinken-hamas-response-creates-space-for-agreement-netanyahu-slams-delusional-demands/0000018d-868c-d0de-af8d-8ebc4d630000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的妻子出庭听取以色列前总检察长在总理腐败案审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-in-court-to-hear-israels-former-ag-testify-in-pms-graft-trial/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff9c6130000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡因接受好莱坞大亨和澳大利亚商人价值数十万谢克尔的礼物而受审，其中最著名的是雪茄和香槟，他否认了这些指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 22:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-in-court-to-hear-israels-former-ag-testify-in-pms-graft-trial/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff9c6130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，以色列军队在袭击西岸难民营时打死三名武装巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/israeli-forces-kill-three-armed-palestinians-in-raid-on-west-bank-refugee-camp-idf-says/0000018d-852f-d0de-af8d-8d3f35ac0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，其中一名目标人员被描述为难民营的“高级特工”，涉嫌向以色列军队开枪并参与恐怖活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/israeli-forces-kill-three-armed-palestinians-in-raid-on-west-bank-refugee-camp-idf-says/0000018d-852f-d0de-af8d-8d3f35ac0000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的人质含泪敦促内塔尼亚胡确保释放被哈马斯扣押的剩余以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-hamas-demands-as-freed-israeli-hostages-plea-him-to-avoid-moral-stain/0000018d-8501-df76-a1fd-cff1a7980000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在新闻发布会上表示，“后天就是哈马斯的后天”，并坚称“全面胜利”是他唯一可以接受的结果。一名72岁的获释人质向总理呼吁：“如果你继续‘瓦解哈马斯’的路线，就不会有任何人质可以拯救了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-hamas-demands-as-freed-israeli-hostages-plea-him-to-avoid-moral-stain/0000018d-8501-df76-a1fd-cff1a7980000</guid></item><item><title>马克龙向 10 月 7 日遇难者家属提供了内塔尼亚胡不会提供的东西</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</link><description>在以色列，仍被哈马斯扣押的 100 多名人质的家人被迫乞求与内阁成员会面，并了解停火协议的最新进展，以便让他们回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔加强对执法部门的控制，以色列媒体顾问接受警方讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</link><description>伊齐克·埃尔罗夫（Itzik Elrov）发布了一张照片，其中以色列交通部长穿着一件用沾满鲜血的爆米花制成的连衣裙。一名高级观察员表示，警方对他的讯问反映出本-格维尔的“帮派风气”对以色列警察的影响日益加深</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 19:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 124 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</link><description>哈马斯提出 135 天停火计划 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡称哈马斯提议“妄想” ■ 由卡塔尔/埃及斡旋的新一轮人质释放协议谈判定于周四开始 ■ 沙特阿拉伯表示，如果没有独立的巴勒斯坦国，就不可能与以色列实现正常化■ 战争开始 124 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 18:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部夸耀巴勒斯坦 LGBTQ 庇护裁决；内政部长寻求逆转</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</link><description>特拉维夫的一名法官最近裁定，因性取向受到威胁的巴勒斯坦人可以在以色列申请庇护。外交部发布了一条推文庆祝这一裁决，然后将其删除</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦国能在经济上实现生存吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</link><description>约旦河西岸和加沙拥有一些资产可以用来建设繁荣的经济，但负债也更大。拜登的计划未能解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:49:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</guid></item><item><title>法国为哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击事件受害者举行全球首个悼念仪式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</link><description>42 名法裔以色列遇难者的约 100 名亲属参加了在巴黎举行的活动，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 宣布“今天有 6800 万法国公民哀悼”。一位悲伤的母亲告诉媒体，“在以色列，我们感觉自己被忽视了，感谢法国，我的女儿不会被忘记”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</guid></item><item><title>“未经证实的指控”：英国第四频道猛烈抨击以色列对近东救济工程处的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</link><description>针对联合国巴勒斯坦难民救济机构的指控是在一份以色列情报简报中提出的，最初是在《华尔街日报》上报道的。英国第四频道声称“没有证据”证明以色列对近东救济工程处工作人员的指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:28:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</guid></item><item><title>停火协议将是哈马斯的巨大胜利，但以色列别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</link><description>2011 年，我参与谈判的哈马斯与以色列人质协议规定，以 1,000 多名巴勒斯坦囚犯换取一名以色列士兵。这本应该是以色列最后一次不得不赎回其公民，但今天，哈马斯占了上风</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</guid></item></channel></rss>